    <TestGroupDocumentation>
        <Title>
   	class declaration to customize the binding of a schema component to
   	an element class, value class or interface/implementation class (valid schema with bindinfo)
        </Title>
        <Description>
   	Test verifies constraint of class customization: Local Element Declaration To Java Element
 	A class customization on local element reference must result in an invalid
	customization since a local element reference is never bound to a Java Element class.
        </Description>
